Capacent to acquire Capacent Island












Friday, 3 Feb 2017 01:14am EST Capacent Holding AB (publ) : Said on Thursday signed agreement to acquire 62.5 pct of Capacent ehf (Capacent Island) . Initial purchase price is estimated at 9.25 million Swedish crowns ($1 million) with potential earn-out in two years of up to 15.3 million crowns depending on Capacent Island's EBITDA in 2017 and 2018 .Initial purchase price to be paid partly in cash (5.89 million crowns) and partly in form of non-cash issue (3.36 million crowns). 



