Capacent Holding AB (publ), Annual General Meeting, Mar 31, 2017
Mar 28 17
Capacent Holding AB (publ), Annual General Meeting, Mar 31, 2017, at 09:00 Central European Standard Time. Location: Snickarbacken 4 Stockholm Sweden Agenda: To consider presentation of the annual report and audit report and the consolidated audit report; to consider income statement and balance sheet and the consolidated balance sheet, and the disposition of profits shown in the balance sheet; to discharge the board and CEO; to determine the number of members and deputies; to determine Board of directors and auditors; to consider election of Board of directors, any deputies and auditors; and to consider resolution to authorize the Board to resolve on issues of shares, warrants and / or convertibles.


